name: Fragments Necklace
description:
This necklace was created using a handmade precious metal clay(PMC) fragment,sterling silver spacers, Sterling silver handmade closure,sterling chain and gemstones which may include;Agate – Black, Tree and Green Spot; Amazonite; Aventurine – Green and Red; Bronzonite; Citrine; Carnelian; Hichorite; numerous kinds of Jasper - Picture Stone, Red Picture Stone, Poppy, Brecated, Conglomerate, Picasso; Lapis Lazuli; Obsidian – Rainbow, Mahogany; Opalite; Sodalite; Tiger Eye - Blue, Yellow, Gold; Turquoise - Stabilized, Yellow, African, Imperial; Quartz - Crystal, Pink, Rose, Cherry, Black and Blue Rutilated. 

Necklace length 20-22 adjustable
Drop @ 3 inches(L)

Ships Priority with delivery confirmation, arrives gift boxed.

name: Rosary Style Necklace
description:
Natural turquoise is bezel set in 22 gauge sterling silver, accented with a vintage copper bead,turquoise discs, turquoise beads, and carved bone beads, sterling spacers and vintage religious medallion.
The piece is finished with a handmade sterling silver clasp.

Etched on the back Sentiment reads "all things work for the greater good."

chain measures; 18 1/2 inches (L)
top of turquoise to bottom of medallion 3 3/4 inches(L)

Arrives gift boxed, ships priority with delivery confirmation.
